title: Steve Coleman Chicago Residency Interview
description:
Steve Coleman talks about the concept behind doing residencies and outreach, in the United States and around the world, through his non-profit organization, M-Base Concepts, Inc. Steve Coleman and Five Elements have presented successful residencies all around the country. These residencies are designed to generate energy in the areas where they occur, educate local musicians and introduce audiences to creative and progressive music.

Past residencies have taken place in Chicago, Detroit, Philadelphia, Los Angeles, San Francisco, Oakland, Havana (Cuba), Salvador da Bahia (Brazil), Paris (France), Montpellier (France), Saint-Louis (Senegal), Abidjan (Côte d’Ivoire), Chennai (India).

To support our residencies with donations (any amount), please go to https://www.paypal.me/mbaseconcepts
or for more information - contact info1@m-base.org

Also, please join our creative music community at http://m-base.net, if you are interested in exploring new perspectives in creative music (instructional videos, concerts footage, blogs, conference calls, etc. - registration is free).

Follow me on Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/mbase1235/
